1-07T00:22:38.000Z","msg":"愛與和平拯救金木<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6887c46a5abb3d98ad7b8ecb558efed350a76cab","tid":460353,"uid":155133,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:09:02.000Z","msg":"話金木廢既其實有冇留心睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢半人半食鬼 不嬲兩邊都唔想殺<br />\n再者佢加速緊老化都堅持唔共食<br />\n宜家根本實力廢過流島個陣<br />\n冇再生 變唔返人手<br />\n<br />\n佢仲係佐佐木個陣同鈴屋係朋友<br />\n點會想殺佢<br />\n比人斬成人棍個內心世界都係度掙扎緊<br />\n殺唔殺人<br />\n要保護董香先暴走<br />\n其實講真佢季季都係loop<br />\n有野保護先暴走啦<br />\n<br />\n今集隻臭雞就黎出動煽動<br />\n班食屍鬼出黎幫王報仇<br />\n<br />\n雖然佢輸得好柒<br />\n可以輸得型少少<br />\n但劇情黎講我覺得OK<br />\n又帶出返永近 和修 嘉納"},{"pid":"779aab4582a6ec8cd9827a6c784d13040280508f","tid":460353,"uid":155133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:15:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>月山巨人化？</blockquote><br />\n應該係<br />\n佢有排瘋狂共食<br />\n甲赫赫者化"},{"pid":"99148124cebf4d8bdad67e99103a1e6805daa7e6","tid":460353,"uid":39478,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:15:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好彩最後一頁係月山，如果係董香真係嚇死人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最後一頁尾幾格唔係董香咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個pat陰係另一邊架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a17128c410688de3489e179b917893758478485","tid":460353,"uid":48042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:47:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>伊鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n胸懷大痣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n由上季開始已經好留意伊鳥對波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有集回憶拉起條裙引誘人 最後個集又倒血酒落對波到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw今集劇情進展終於快返啲 開始交待加納同永近</blockquote><br />\n邊集<img src=